				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Reaction after Arabella, a tiefling child, is killed by the druid Kagha's serpent in the grove. \r\n\r\nRequires two speakers.\r\n\r\nSpeaker 1 is the character who was in the dialog and had opportunity to stop it. (May have tried and failed or simply refrained from acting)\r\n\r\nSpeaker 2 is an accompanying character, they may have an opinionated line regarding the outcome according to their own beliefs."
				}
